title: Cowboys Don't Cry
description:
Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth recap MNF between the Cowboys and Giants. They preview Thursday night’s matchup between the Dolphins and Bengals. Can the Dolphins go 4-0? Plus, did Mina accidentally put a curse on the Chargers last week? We have proof. And Mina and Domonique give their Winners and Woofs for Week 3.
